build_shaders.py is a helper script for compiling glsl shaders for vulkan

To use it, pass the directory containing the files you want to compile after -s, an output directy after -o and optionally a -r argumentif you want to recursively compile shaders in subfolders

Example:

build_shaders.py -s C:\Projects\PuffinEngine\shaders\vulkan -o C:\Projects\PuffinEngine\bin\vulkan -r